properties.sfomuseum:description: Stock certificate issued to Fairchild Aviation Corporation for 100 shares of Aviation Corporation of the Americas; certificate number 2137, dated January 22, 1929; green and white; official corporate seal impression and original signatures of E. S. (Sally) Swaggerty, Assistant Secretary, and J. T. Trippe, Vice President; signed on reverse by C. S. Reed on September 25, 1929; countersigned January 22, 1929 by The Equitable Trust Company of New York, registered January 22, 1929 by The New York Trust Company; certificate note by American Bank Note Company; document defaced by hole punch cancellation at left and lower right.
